Invocation Name: food pal
des:
Foodpal gives you all the nutrition information about any food.
Foodpal gives you how much calories are present in any food per quantity.
Foodpal also gives you how much protein,fats are present in any food per quantity.
Just say alexa ask foodpal for nutrition information
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
